---
title: Maple-Mustard Steak with Broccoli and Sweet Potatoes
description: Best friends forever – steak, mustard and maple will always
be our favourite pals! This oh-so-Canadian combo of maple and mustard on tender sirloin won't let you down. Hearty veggies complement the sweet and zesty glaze perfectly!
